==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: míng bù zhèng, zé yán bù shùn
===Etymology===
From the ''[[w:Analects of Confucius|Analects of Confucius]]'': If the name is incorrect, then words will not follow.
===Proverb===
'''[[名]][[不]][[正]]，[[則]][[言]][[不]][[順]]'''
# You must first properly define an issue in order to talk about it intelligently.
===Alternate forms===
[[名不正，则言不顺]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
